I DO NOT CONSENT! & I WILL NEVER BE SILENCED! // Hey @thisisbillgates My ancestors already died by the hand of colonialism once and I’ll be dead myself before I let you cast out another generation of LIGHT! The first round of volunteers were slaughtered well guess-the-fuck-what??!! WE’RE BACK ~ CUZ WE NEVER LEFT! When you killed us, our spirits were reborn amongst the plants and animals. We became the trees that offered you shade and the sweet flowers who’s fragrance rode through the winds.. Likewise we became the fires that tore through the forest and the floods that re shaped the land... You cannot escape the light @thisisbillgates & you WILL NOT kill anymore innocent people! •
